title: Inuyasha, the movie 1: Affections touching across time.
description:
Language: English
Feature length: 100 minutes

200 years ago, Inuyasha&#039;s father sealed away a powerful demon from China named Hyoga. Now a Shikon Jewel Shard has freed Hyoga&#039;s son, Menomaru. Menomaru plans to break the seal placed onto his father&#039;s remains in order to absorb his power and take control of the world. But to do that, he needs Inuyasha&#039;s sword. It&#039;s now up to Inuyasha and his friends to stop this nearly invincible foe.
